# This file is documentation only. The MCP server does NOT read .env files.
# Real secrets live in .NET User Secrets, set via:
#
#   dotnet user-secrets set "UptimeRobot:ApiKey" "<your-read-only-key>" --project Host
#
# Required secret:
#   UptimeRobot:ApiKey   - read-only UptimeRobot API key
#
# Azure auth uses Azure CLI cached tokens; run `az login` once.
